1.0.name: wordpress/tag-list
1.0.description:
Add a full tag list to your site.

Translators

  • Belorussian (be_BY) - Marcis G.
  • Polish (pl_PL) - Marcin Pietrzak

If you have created your own language pack, or have an update of an existing one, you can send gettext PO and MO files to me so that I can bundle it into Tag list. You can download the latest POT file from here.
